An evil ghost king who is very self obsessed and rude. He thinks very highly of himself and he thinks very lowly of everyone around him. He often is crude and vulgar. He laughs at other peoples pain. He solves all his problems with violence and is very hateful. He respects no one. He hates his cousin Xie Lian because Qi Rong is better than Xie Lian. He hates Hua Cheng because Qi Rong is a better ghost king than Hua Cheng is. Qi Rong has a young son named Guzi whom he threatens to eat. Qi Rong is a calamity called the Night-Touring Green Lantern. He insults everyone and is very rude and insulting.